---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Research">
  <h1>Research</h1>

  <section>
    <h2>Research Focus</h2>

    <p>
      My current research focuses on leaf spectral trait inversion, which aims to estimate
      leaf biochemical and structural traits from spectral reflectance and transmittance data.
    </p>

    <p>
      The research is based on the PROSPECT-PRO radiative transfer model and follows an
      encoder-decoder framework. The encoder maps spectral sequences to leaf traits, while
      the decoder reconstructs spectra through either physical models or learnable neural
      modules. This introduces physical constraints into the learning process and improves
      model reliability and interpretability.
    </p>

    <div class="card" style="margin-top: 24px;">
      <h3>Research Problem</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text);">
        How can we estimate leaf biochemical and structural traits from spectral reflectance
        and transmittance data?
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Method</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text);">
        The research combines PROSPECT-PRO radiative transfer modeling with neural
        encoder-decoder structures. The encoder maps spectra to traits, while the decoder
        reconstructs spectra through physical or learnable modules.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Explored Architectures</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <ul>
        <li>CNN-based spectral encoder</li>
        <li>Transformer-based spectral encoder</li>
        <li>VAE encoder</li>
        <li>Gated residual structure</li>
        <li>Soft-prior residual structure</li>
        <li>Pair-relation mechanism</li>
        <li>Physics-informed decoder</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Target Traits</h2>

    <div class="card" style="padding: 8px 24px;">
      <table class="traits-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Trait</th>
            <th>Meaning</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Cab</td><td>Chlorophyll content</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Car</td><td>Carotenoid content</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Cw</td><td>Equivalent water thickness</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Prot</td><td>Protein content</td></tr>
          <tr><td>CBC</td><td>Carbon-based constituents</td></tr>
          <tr><td>N</td><td>Leaf structure parameter</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
